N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 177.5 - Habitat stamp fee

State Regulations

The fee for the habitat stamp shall be $5. One dollar shall
be retained by the license issuing agent as commission, and $4 shall be
deposited in the habitat account authorized by subdivision (h) of section
83
of the

State Finance Law. Notes
